params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM'"

"SELECT " +" M.CUST_CD, " +" M.CUST_NAME, " +" M.CUR_CD, " +" M.EXCH_TYP, " +" M.DETAIL_ROUND_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_CUST M, " +" T_PROJECT T " +"WHERE " +" M.CUST_CD = T.CUST_CD " +" AND T.PROJECT_CD = ? " +" AND M.COMPANY_CD = ?"

"insert into " +" t_project(PROJECT_CD, PROJECT_NAME, CUST_CD, PROJECT_STAT, ACCURACY, VEND_DATE, ASSUME_DLV_DATE, ASSUME_AMOUNT, ASSUME_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES, DLV_LOC_CD, PJ_ORG_CD, PJ_USER_CD, REMARKS1, REMARKS2, REMARKS3, REMARKS4, REMARKS5, OD_COMP_FLG, PJ_CLASS_01_CD, PJ_CLASS_02_CD, PJ_CLASS_03_CD, PJ_CLASS_04_CD, PJ_CLASS_05_CD, PJ_CLASS_06_CD, PJ_CLASS_07_CD, PJ_CLASS_08_CD, PJ_CLASS_09_CD, PJ_CLASS_10_CD, PJ_CLASS_11_CD, PJ_CLASS_12_CD, DEL_FLG) " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, 1, ?, to_date(?, 'yyyy/mm/dd'), to_date(?, 'yyyy/mm/dd'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, nvl(?, 0), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, 0)"
"SELECT " +" T.PROJECT_CD " +"FROM " +" T_PROJECT T " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" T.PROJECT_CD, " +" T.PROJECT_NAME, " +" T.CUST_CD, " +" T.PROJECT_STAT, " +" T.ACCURACY, " +" TO_CHAR(T.VEND_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" TO_CHAR(T.ASSUME_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" TO_CHAR(T.ASSUME_AMOUNT), " +" TO_CHAR(T.ASSUME_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES), " +" T.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" T.PJ_ORG_CD, " +" T.PJ_USER_CD, " +" T.REMARKS1, " +" T.REMARKS2, " +" T.REMARKS3, " +" T.REMARKS4, " +" T.REMARKS5, " +" TO_CHAR(T.OD_COMP_FLG), " +" T.PJ_CLASS_01_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_02_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_03_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_04_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_05_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_06_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_07_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_08_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_09_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_10_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_11_CD, " +" T.PJ_CLASS_12_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(T.MODIFY_COUNT) " +"FROM " +" T_PROJECT T " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = ? " +" AND T.DEL_FLG = '0'"

"update " +" t_project " +"set " +" PROJECT_NAME = ?, " +" CUST_CD = ?, " +" PROJECT_STAT = ?, " +" ACCURACY = ?, " +" VEND_DATE = to_date(?, 'yyyy/mm/dd'), " +" ASSUME_DLV_DATE = to_date(?, 'yyyy/mm/dd'), " +" ASSUME_AMOUNT = ?, " +" ASSUME_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES = ?, " +" DLV_LOC_CD = ?, " +" PJ_ORG_CD = ?, " +" PJ_USER_CD = ?, " +" REMARKS1 = ?, " +" REMARKS2 = ?, " +" REMARKS3 = ?, " +" REMARKS4 = ?, " +" REMARKS5 = ?, " +" OD_COMP_FLG = nvl(?, 0), " +" PJ_CLASS_01_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_02_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_03_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_04_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_05_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_06_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_07_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_08_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_09_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_10_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_11_CD = ?, " +" PJ_CLASS_12_CD = ? " +"WHERE " +" PROJECT_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD, " +" CUST_CD, " +" DLV_LOC_CD, " +" DLV_LOC_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_CUST_BASE " +"WHERE " +" DLV_LOC_CD = ? " +" AND CUST_CD = ? " +" AND COMPANY_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD, " +" ORG_CD, " +" ORG_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_ORG " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND ORG_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" USER_CD, " +" USER_NAME " +"FROM " +" USER_MST " +"WHERE " +" USER_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" T.ODR_NO " +"FROM " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC T " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = ? " +" AND T.ESTIMATE_NO = ? " +" AND T.DETAL_NO = ?"
"SELECT " +" T.ODR_CMPLT_FLG " +"FROM " +" T_ODR T " +"WHERE " +" T.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND T.DEL_FLG = '0'"
"SELECT " +" T.ODR_CMPLT_FLG " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK T " +"WHERE " +" T.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND T.DEL_FLG = '0'"
"UPDATE " +" T_PROJECT T " +"SET " +" T.DEL_FLG = '1' " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = ?"
"select " +" 'PJ' || to_char(lpad(SEQ_PJ_CD.Nextval, 10, '0')) " +"from " +" dual"
"SELECT " +" M.CUST_CD, " +" M.CUR_CD, " +" M.EXCH_TYP, " +" M.DETAIL_ROUND_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_CUST M " +"WHERE " +" M.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M.COMPANY_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" CUR.CUR_CD, " +" CUR.CUR_UNIT " +"FROM " +" M_CUR CUR, " +" M_CUST CUST " +"WHERE " +" CUR.CUR_CD = CUST.CUR_CD " +" AND CUST.CUST_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" T.PROJECT_CD, " +" T.ESTIMATE_NO, " +" T_DETAIL.DETAL_NO, " +" T_DETAIL.ESTIMATE_TYPE " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE T, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL T_DETAIL " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = T_DETAIL.PROJECT_CD " +" AND T.ESTIMATE_STAT = '2' " +" AND T.ESTIMATE_NO = T_DETAIL.ESTIMATE_NO " +" AND T.PROJECT_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" M.CUST_CD, " +" M.CUST_NAME, " +" M.CUR_CD, " +" M.EXCH_TYP, " +" M.DETAIL_ROUND_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_CUST M " +"WHERE " +" M.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M.CUST_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" T.PROJECT_CD, " +" T.ESTIMATE_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE T " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" T.PROJECT_CD, " +" T.ESTIMATE_NO, " +" T_DETAIL.DETAL_NO, " +" T_DETAIL.ESTIMATE_TYPE " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE T, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL T_DETAIL " +"WHERE " +" T.PROJECT_CD = T_DETAIL.PROJECT_CD " +" AND T.ESTIMATE_STAT = '2' " +" AND T.ESTIMATE_NO = T_DETAIL.ESTIMATE_NO " +" AND T_DETAIL.ODR_FLG = 0 " +" AND T.PROJECT_CD = ?"
